dct_description_sm: A map of certain real estate in the fifth ward of the City of New Brunswick, north of Somerset St. formerly of Abraham Suydam, Esq. and by him conveyed with other property to James Lorimar Graham on June 25, 1838. Some lots are shaded in pink.
tissue encapsulated, mounted on linen, partially colored with notes in pencil.
